metadata.description:
A piece of my heart and a Digital Fashion Artwork.
With a bunch of colored lights and textures I give life to my 3D clothes inspired by the greek goddess Nemesis with gothic aesthetics.

Exclusive collection of 1/6 Different Designs.

This Digital Artwork comes with 3 Physical Prints 120x90cm. (Free shipping)

You may also have early access to the new collections, and new launches. 

Thank you so much for your support <3
Alexa
